\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The University of Stellenbosch is a public higher education provider offering in the contact mode. The institution is currently offering a BSc in Forestry and Natural Resources. This application was submitted in April 2011. It was evaluated but could not be processed because it didn\'27t have PQM clearance. We have recently received the PQM clearance and therefore finalising the process. \cell \pard 

